node.text:
We’re launching a Tuesday TIP OF THE WEEK series to help answer some commonly asked questions from our community! Today we’re kicking off with our friend @takebetterphotosofyourdog 📸 

Every dog deserves a great portrait. But it’s not always possible to hire a professional photographer, and most people don’t own a DSLR or mirrorless camera. Luckily, cell phones come with pretty good built-in cameras these days!

Watch this video for a list of tips that'll help you be a better photographer - with your cell phone! Be sure to ready our blog (LINK IN BIO) or download the guide on www.dogphototips.com 

We’ll focus one week a month on how to take better photos of your dog, so leave your questions in the comments and tune back in next month for the answers! 

Check out more tips from Take Better Photos of Your Dog: @takebetterphotosofyourdog
Cover photo: @marshygsp 

#dogphotography #takebetterphotosofyourdog #photographytips #tuesdaytip #dogsofinstagram #tipoftheweek #phototips #dogphotos #dogphotoshoot

node.title: How To Take Better Photos of Your Dog With Your Phone

Did you know 17.6 billion pounds of plastic are dumped into the oceans each year? That’s like 57,000 blue whales! Join our #EarthsBestFriend Cleanup Challenge in partnership with @projectblusocial to help make life better for pets, people, and the planet!

JOIN THE MOVEMENT AND EVERYONE WINS! We’re partnering with @projectblusocial and other sustainable brands around the world such as @pelacase,@barxbypet, @theouai, @farmbrandinspires, @mudjeans, @goldilocksgoods , @shamelesspets, @brooklyngrooming, and @4Earthapp to bring awareness to the best practices for reducing waste. 

Submit a photo of you and your pet cleaning up your community for the chance to win over $1,500 worth of eco-friendly products that will make you feel as good as you look. PLUS, every entry gets a tree planted through @onetreeplanted. Contest open from April 22-May 22. 

🌏 LINK IN BIO TO SUBMIT 🌍

Huge shoutout to our amazing @dogsofinstagram community for helping clean up and protect our planet! In no particular order:

@kaleiahskyy @apupcalledmika @dognamedbrewski @petitepokey @chewy_bernedoodle @darrelthedoge @dextersvida @puppies.n.pinot @frankandgary @gerti.b_ @kip.and.his.tongue @leo.eat.sleep.retrieve @leothemountainboy @lucasandperla_theiggies @luna_the_yorkiepoo @pepe_the_golden @rigby.corgi @sunnysbestlife @thismudderfluffer @whenashmetbowser @amyjaym 

🎥 edits: @tyleroo 

#earthsbestfriend #earthday #earthdaycleanupchallenge #gogreen #sustainability #ecofriendly #ecofriendlypetproducts #sustainablepetproducts #ecofriendlybeautyproducts #sustainablebeautyproducts #reduceplastic #carbonneutral #carbonpositive #positivechange #projectblu #dogsofinstagram

This giveaway is hosted by @DogsOfInstagram and ProjectBlu, in partnership with OUAI, Pela, Barxby, Farm Brand, Mud Jeans, Shameless Pets, Brooklyn Grooming, Goldilocks Goods, and 4Earth. Privacy Policy can be found on Sweepstakes landing page. This Giveaway is not sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with Instagram. Giveaway will start April 22 (12:00am PST) and end May 22nd (11:59pm PST). Must be 18+. Prizes limited to U.S. residents. Featured photos open internationally.

node.text:
By now, you've probably heard how CBD can be beneficial for both humans and pets alike. For those new to the conversation, CBD is a derived from hemp or cannabis and does not contain THC, which is the substance that produces a high for its users. 

In 2018, a Cornell study reported 80% of osteoarthritis dogs who used CBD showed “significant improvement in pain levels and quality of life”. 

In a world where too many pets are homeless, abandoned, or returned, CBD seems to offer a ray of hope. The potential to steady a dog’s nerves long enough to charm a family, relieve a joint pain, aid in separation anxiety, or help behave when meeting new people could make all the difference in a pet’s life. Incorporating CBD into a consistent routine is one practice that can support this transition and pave the way for calm, happy families. 

Link in bio to read more about how CBD can help animals or donate a CBD product to a shelter pet through @welovecuddly! 

#dogsofinstagram #cbdforpets #cbdhealth #theanxiouspet #releasethepeace #relaxandroll @theanxiouspet

node.title: Free to Be CBD: How Hemp Products Can Help Rescue Animals

When your furrriends surprise you with the sweetest gift 😭♥️ We just have to say thank you one more time to each and every single pawson who reached out to wish us a happy Ten Year Anniversary! We had SO much fun celebrating and pawting with everyone 🥳 Thank you for such a wonderful ten years, and cheers to many more to come! 🎊 #doicheerstotenyears

node.text:
CHEERS TO TEN YEARS 🥳 We are overwhelmed with the love from all of you! Thanks so making this decade so amazing, and we can’t wait to continue bringing together the dogs of Instagram for the next decade! 🎉 Swipe to the end to see our incredible surprise (organized by @puppies.n.pinot and edited by @apupcalledmika) from some of our furriends ♥️

Huge shoutout to everyone who tagged us and used #doicheerstotenyears in your photos this month! 

Congrats to the following furriend who won free swag from us 🎊:
@2husketeers, @baileythequarendoggo, @mojothebulldox , @thismudderfluffer, @thiscrazydoghouse, @stewdawahwah, @rockynycmorkie, @furry_cousins, @boba_the_mini_pup, @great.dane.gus, @rambothepuppy, @kip.and.his.tongue, @dognamedbrewski, @frankandgary, @smileyriley_nalagram, @stanleyzthepomchi 

(We’ll follow up with you all individually for shipping!)

We can’t say thank you enough! What a wonderful community to be a part of and celebrate the good doggos all around the world! #doicheerstotenyears 💖

node.text:
Happy birthday to us! 🥳 My oh my how the years have flown by! We’ve been blown away by the love and support of this absolutely amazing community of dog lovers over the last decade. We are so thankful for each and every person who has engaged with us over the years. We truly couldn’t have done it without you! 

Thanks for helping us spread the pawsitivity and dog love to everyone around the world. Cheers to more years to come! WE LOVE YOU AND ALL YOUR DOGGOS ♥️🐾

Stay tuned for our fun prizes and giveaways today along with our IG Lives: 

- Meet our Founders, Ahmed and Ashley 11am PST / 2pm ET
- @sunnysbestlife 1pm PST / 4pm ET
- @darrelthedoge 2pm PST / 5pm ET
- @apupcalledmika 3pm PST / 6pm ET

Thanks for celebrating with us furriends! 

📸: @darrelthedoge and @myislandheelers, y’all are the best for making these videos for us!! 

#doicheerstotenyears #dogsofinstagram #pawtytime

node.text:
We turn TEN this week, and you know we have a few fun TRICKS planned to celebrate! We’re teaming up with our pawesome pals @thesupercollies and @pupprschool for the ULTIMUTT TRICK CONTEST! Submit at dogsof.com - link in bio! 

Top Ten will be featured on our page and THREE lucky winners will receive a 1-year subscription to @pupprschool!

@pupprschool makes it easy to train your dog at home! Puppr includes step-by-step video instructions to help you teach your dog basic obedience like “sit” and “stay” to advanced tricks like “fetch leash” and “sit pretty”. Great for both new and experienced dog owners.

3 selected winners will receive a 1-year subscription to Puppr Premium (value of $99), which includes access to:
- Over 100 tricks and lessons taught by Sara Carson & The Super Collies
- Puppr Masterclasses that provide in-depth guidance on topics like leash training taught by certified experts
- Live chat with our team of world-class trainers to get your training questions answered

🌟Download Puppr at www.puppr.app and use referral code "DOGSOFIG" to unlock a free lesson pack! 🌟

Be sure to check out @thesupercolliesmom’s new book, Super Dog Tricks, available for pre - order and out in January! 

#DOICHEERSTOTENYEARS #dogtricks #dogtricksofinstagram #dogtraining #dogtrickcontest #trickoftheweek

node.text:
Raise a hand (or paw) if you’re ready for a vacation! As part of our Ten Year Anniversary celebration, we’re giving away a VACATION PACKAGE from our friends @trustedhousesitters🛩️

Head to the link in our bio to enter to our GOING PLACES GIVEAWAY! 🛫

🏆 1 Grand Prize winner will receive 2 roundtrip tickets to fly anywhere in the world ($3,000 value). Offer Valid for 12 months.

Giveaway ends on July 31st (11:59pm PST). Must be 18+.

This giveaway is not sponsored, endorsed, administered by, or associated with Instagram or Facebook.

📸: @fallon.finn.ollie 

#DOIcheerstotenyears #giveaway #tot #tongueouttuesday #freeplanetickets #travel #vacationpackage #vacationgiveaway#entertowin #goingplacesgiveaway #trustedhousesitters

node.text:
Need some motivation to start your Monday? Meet @dexterdogouray, after an accident left him with just two functional legs, he taught himself how to walk again. Here he is being cheered on as the star of his town’s 4th of July Parade 🎆 

What an inspiration! Double tap to show this guy some love ♥️ 

#dogsofinstagram #motivationmonday #mondaymotivation #doicheerstotenyears #inspirationaldog #twoleggeddog
